What you need to know:

Meanwhile, Kimathi also sent a message of condolences to Sports Cabinet Secretary Amina Mohamed following the death of her brother Esmael Mohammed Jibril.Jibril, a prominent Nairobi businessman, died on Monday while receiving treatment in India.Jibril’s body is expected Wednesday ahead of his burial the same day.CS Amina is also a member of the FIA’s World Motor Sport Council and is key to the WRC Safari Rally’s preparations.